  <spirit:version>1.0</spirit:version>
  <spirit:description>
    AXI4-Lite slave register file for the 2D GPU Accelerator.
    Exposes 8 × 32-bit control/status registers to the ARM PS.
    Generates draw commands and IRQ to the PL drawing engine.
  </spirit:description>

